<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>WordProblemApp</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container container-narrow">
  <div class="hero-unit">
    <h1>Holly - Tenth Generation AI Computer</h1>
    <h2>IQ: 6000</h2>
    <p class="text-info">Well she used to have an IQ of 6000. Now she can answer any question as long as it's in the right format.</p>

    <p>What is <strong>[number] {operation} [number]</strong> <em></em> ?</p>

    <p>Any number of additional {operation} [number] pairs may be chained on to the end of the above expression.</p>

  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid contents">
    <%= yield %>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
